{"tid":1545451,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［疑問/建議］9.7 和你塞3.0，有咩意見集中講","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T02:44:35.000Z","uid":234159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"200749b0f4c0f2af6805c095998d60f1b92e01e6","tid":1545451,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:10:12.000Z","msg":"我睇咗更新版的安排。我係有幾個問題，想問咗搞手先決定去/唔去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 點解仲要巴士總站集合？你地諗緊咩？<br />\n如果封鎖巴士總站，逐個check 有機票先可出，點算？上次就係所有人在同一個位，防暴一來個個都唔知佢地做得出啲咩。最安全係，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊客喺邊我地喺邊</span></span>，直接排T1/T2有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n2. 機鐵一定要有人搞<br />\n上次稍微有啲成績（有個別flight cancel、塞住離開機場的路）絕對係因為機鐵俾人破壞咗，佢先運唔到遊客出來，局住要開番巴士、的士。如果今次一樣，入到機場的先搭得機鐵走而鎖出面交通，我地可以等住俾人拉。<br />\n<br />\n3. 唔好再搞東涌站<br />\n建議當日唔好跳閘，唔好搞站，乖乖扮遊客。如果再因搞站而俾咗個藉口提早封站，又會東涌大圍捕"},{"pid":"942ef9af4e46b31fbf440a614b5bc1786eb4317d","tid":1545451,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93a8de6d91c918e73daeb8660258ec32dcc170a2","tid":1545451,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:43:46.000Z","msg":"推 真心問"},{"pid":"427ca4c5bc68fa7bc0f835ffb8cae1342b25605e","tid":1545451,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:43:59.000Z","msg":"大家有意見都可提"},{"pid":"95301e40df71ec2716ce5ddbf